name: Intelligent Design (Purple)
description:
God blessed them and said to them, “Be fruitful and increase in number; fill the earth and subdue it. Rule over the fish in the sea and the birds in the sky and over every living dinosaur that moves on the ground.” 

This is a tribute to a great inspiration of mine. Someone who’s passion and imagination are never overshadowed by reason or logic. 


Printed on American Apparel 100% cotton
